Package: timenow
Title: Quick Timezone-Aware Timestamps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Sumner", email = "mdsumner@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simple helpers to report the current time in UTC and your local
    timezone, with sensible detection heuristics when the system timezone is UTC.
    Supports fuzzy matching of timezone names like "Perth Australia".
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    clock
